
                        Section 4 - Notes
                     Greeting Hello Service
                            
$ cd greeting

$ cat docker-compose.yaml 
version: '3'
services:
  hello:
    image: alpine:latest
    command: [/bin/echo, 'Hello from alpine!']

$ docker-compose up
Creating network "greeting_default" with the default driver
Creating greeting_hello_1 ... 
Creating greeting_hello_1 ... done
Attaching to greeting_hello_1
hello_1  | Hello from alpine!
greeting_hello_1 exited with code 0

$ docker-compose ps
      Name                   Command              State    Ports
----------------------------------------------------------------
greeting_hello_1   /bin/echo Hello from alpine!   Exit 0  

$ docker-compose up
Starting greeting_hello_1 ... 
Starting greeting_hello_1 ... done
Attaching to greeting_hello_1
hello_1  | Hello from alpine!
greeting_hello_1 exited with code 0








